	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap. ([- - -] L. f. Cn. n. Claudus; G.'s name entire); Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod. (K. Quinctius et L. Genucius); Degrassi, 40f., 114, 430f. Genucius probably began military operations against Rhegium this year (see 270, Consuls)." .
